data.description: Welcome to 298 Hill Crest Circle, Hiram, GA! This stunning home offers the perfect combination of comfort, style, and functionality, and the largest floor plan available in this community. Boasting a desirable location in the heart of Hiram, this property presents an incredible opportunity for families, professionals, and investors alike. You’ll be captivated by the charming curb appeal and well-maintained landscaping courtesy of the HOA. Step inside to discover a spacious and inviting interior flooded with natural light. The open concept floor plan seamlessly connects the formal dining area, living room and kitchen, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The modern kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek countertops, ample cabinetry, and center island. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or enjoying a quick snack, this kitchen offers everything you need for a convenient cooking experience. The huge primary suite boasts a sitting area, ensuite bathroom soaking tub and large walk-in closet. Three additional generously sized bedrooms, a large loft and full bathroom can also be found on the upper level, providing plenty of space for family members or guests. Step outside to the backyard oasis, where you'll find a private patio area perfect for hosting BBQs, relaxing, or enjoying your morning coffee. The large fenced yard offers endless possibilities for gardening and outdoor activities. The two car garage boasts new garage doors and EV charging. There’s not much to do once you move in with these upgrades; New roof, motherboard/vent motors in HVAC system, dual thermostat HVAC, upgraded faucets and fixtures, home security system through Greystone Power and ring doorbell/camera. And if that isn’t enough, the Highland Falls community includes a pool, clubhouse, gym, and kids play area. Conveniently located near a variety of shopping, dining, movies, entertainment options, Silver Comet trails, Wellstar Hospital, and all that Hiram has to offer. Additionally, the home is within close proximity to I75/575 and I20/285 making commuting a breeze. Don't miss your chance to own this fantastic home and make 298 Hill Crest Circle your new address.
